channel.description: Resources Slides Video Script Hello and welcome to the week 13 announcements video for CIS 527 and CC510 in fall 2024. This week you should be working on lab six, which is due on Friday. So make sure you get your grading time scheduled sometime this week to get that turned in. We’re also going to have our fourth discussion session this Wednesday. So make sure you get those questions posted before two o’clock that day.
